ss the relative interface thickness error and\nthe relative surface tension force error with respect to the convective\ndistortion parameter. Two- and three-dimensional rising bubble cases are\nfurther simulated to examine the effectiveness of the proposed model on the\nvolume-preserving mean curvature flow and the interface-preserving capability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Jul 2020 07:51:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-17"}
