 of disagreement is large. The\nexperiments also show strong ability to capture the complex spatial\ncharacteristics of annotators' mistakes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Jul 2020 11:03:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Aug 2020 12:22:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 4 Aug 2020 12:18:45 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 6 Aug 2020 10:26:51 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 23 Oct 2020 12:15:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-26"}
