ed resource planning\nmodel in a top-down step, that would select from these shortlisted projects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Jul 2020 12:53:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Dec 2021 13:56:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-17"}
